OL,7,FMurdoch said Southwick Church has a
OL,8,Fgrowing congregation, healthy
OL,9,Fattendances, is well-funded and in a
OL,10,Fsound state of repair.
OL,12,FAnd he criticised a lack of
OL,13,Fconsultation on draft plans for a
OL,14,Fshake-up in the Presbytery of the
OL,15,FSouth West.
