OL,6,F"The real fear for people in this area
OL,7,Fis that there are a good number of
OL,8,Ffolk who are brought to church by
OL,9,Ffriends, and an extra six or seven
OL,10,Fmiles may be too far for many.
OL,12,F"You could understand that in a city
OL,13,Fwhere there may be four or five
OL,14,Fchurches within a radius of three or
OL,15,Ffiles square miles.
OL,17,F"But in a rural setting with six or
OL,18,Fseven miles between churches it will
OL,19,Fhave a very negative impact."
