OL,6,FIt said: "Southwick Church is the home
OL,7,Fof a dedicated and loyal, congregation
OL,8,Fwho love this holy place and value its
OL,9,Ftranquillity.
OL,11,F"But now, with no consultation with
OL,12,Fthe congregation, the Presbytery of
OL,13,Fthe South West has decided that this
OL,14,Fdelightful place of worship is to be
OL,15,Fabandoned.
OL,17,F"It seems as though a random high-
OL,18,Flevel decision has not taken any
OL,19,Faccount of the local situation."
