OL,6,FChristine Murray, presbytery clerk of
OL,7,Fthe Presbytery of the South West, said
OL,8,FSouthwick had been invited to present
OL,9,Fthe case for their building being
OL,10,Fretained.
OL,12,FShe said: "Following the decision
OL,13,Fbeing taken to approve the new mission
OL,14,Fplan and close this church there was
OL,15,Fthen an opportunity for the matter to
OL,16,Fbe reviewed.
OL,18,F"Southwick applied for such a review,
OL,19,Fand submitted their arguments to the
OL,20,Fcommittee, which is independent of the
OL,21,FPresbytery of the South West.
