OL,6,F"The review application was
OL,7,Funsuccessful, and the decision of the
OL,8,Fpresbytery to close this building in
OL,9,F2027 was upheld.
OL,11,F"It is open to any congregation to
OL,12,Fbring evidence of new, sustainable
OL,13,Fmissional growth to the committee at
OL,14,Ftime of review and to present an
OL,15,Fargument as to how their position has
OL,16,Fso changed in the intervening period
OL,17,Fthat the decision to close should be
OL,18,Freconsidered."
